islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:19:05.000Z","msg":"分析: 唯一救埋大方法 -- 開花<br />\n<br />\n對家優勢:<br />\n武器精良<br />\n<br />\n對家缺點:<br />\n只有不足1萬防暴<br />\n唔敢入校園(圍而不攻斷吾糧草，但24小時內仲安全)<br />\n現時大部分武器，人手都集中於九龍<br />\n<br />\n結論: 人家有槍，一個可打100個，但係大型武器(eg水炮車)都集中於埋大，但其他地方(如狗聯辨，或各大狗屋)是最脆弱，利用快閃優勢，只要威脅到其他春袋，對家就要分兵離開埋大"},{"pid":"4db3ec7430494b947c30f5ac184428b006f03211","tid":1733851,"uid":79075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:21:06.000Z","msg":"Pushhhh"},{"pid":"24eb926dd8417de6e966cc71436b97df8938d783","tid":1733851,"uid":79075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:21:33.000Z","msg":"Pussssh"},{"pid":"c3124f30feb8926bacd1136cb89329a47b906a0d","tid":1733851,"uid":79075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:23:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdcdb44e284df075994df2f35ce9854b96b86aa","tid":1733851,"uid":79075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:25:42.000Z","msg":"俾完正皮都幫手推下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33b67d0c7e0a03a88577e444e63348d78a5e89c","tid":1733851,"uid":79075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:27:00.000Z","msg":"推又推"},{"pid":"e3abaa3a0ee433a3dbccc770193c72fa8ce43b51","tid":1733851,"uid":79075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:27:13.000Z","msg":"推兩次"},{"pid":"6abc82d369063150b366d91a8e93336f730c27d2","tid":1733851,"uid":79075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:29:59.000Z","msg":"推 1"},{"pid":"de9f82edc6b0e4ed2947dc9f0006bdb19347813c","tid":1733851,"uid":79075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:30:09.000Z","msg":"推 2"},{"pid":"2595165d2bcd7004b3efa40b126419980213c086","tid":1733851,"uid":79075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s